items.title: Multimodal reinforcement learning with agentic verifier for AI agents
items.summary: Argos improves multimodal RL by evaluating whether an agent’s reasoning aligns with what it observes over time . The approach reduces visual hallucinations and produces more reliable, data-efficient agents for real-world applications . Microsoft Research: Argos is a tool that can be used to train AI agents to be more reliable and efficient .

items.title: Differential Transformer V2
items.summary: Differential Transformer V2 is a two-year-old version of the Transformer Transformer . The Transformer was designed to be able to transform the world's largest Transformers . It is the first of its kind in a series of high-tech vehicles designed for the next generation of Transformers . Transformer has been shown to be in production for the first time in the U.S.

items.title: Introducing Waypoint-1: Real-time interactive video diffusion from Overworld
items.summary: Waypoint-1: Real-time interactive video diffusion from Overworld . Waypoint is a waypoint-like interactive video diffusion from the world of Overworld. It's the first time Waypoint has been used in the world's first interactive video-diffusion toolkit. Waypoint will be available in the U.S. for free .
